        </div>

        <blockquote class="text-base md:text-2xl text-gray-800 text-center leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8 font-medium italic">
          "I am very happy with the results from BrightForge! My site gets more visitors and my business is growing. They explain things clearly and make the process easy. Great service all around."
        </blockquote>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">
            R
          </div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="text-base md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110455532132624140129/reviews?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">
                RJ GO
              </a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-orange-500 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">Google Review â€¢ Jun 20, 2022</p>
